@startwbs
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 13

title Hotel Booking Management System — Sitemap (Client Routes)

* /
** Home (Rooms List)
*** Room Detail: /rooms/:id
*** Tourist Attractions: /attractions
** Auth
*** Register: /register
*** Login: /login
*** Forgot Password: /reset
*** Reset Password: /reset-password/:token
** User (Protected)
*** Profile: /profile
*** Bookings: /bookings
**** Payment: /bookings/:id/payment
**** Confirmation: /bookings/:id/confirmation
**** Invoice: /invoice/:id
*** Buffets
**** List: /buffets
**** Detail: /buffets/:id
**** Payment: /buffet-bookings/:id/payment
**** Confirmation: /buffet-bookings/:id/confirmation
** Admin (Protected, role=admin)
*** Dashboard: /admin/dashboard
*** Rooms
**** List: /admin/rooms
**** Create: /admin/rooms/create
**** Edit: /admin/rooms/edit/:id
*** Bookings: /admin/bookings
*** Customers
**** List: /admin/customers
**** Detail: /admin/customers/:id
*** Promotions
**** List: /admin/promotions
**** Create: /admin/promotions/create
**** Edit: /admin/promotions/edit/:id
*** Buffet Dinners
**** List: /admin/buffet-dinners
**** Create: /admin/buffet-dinners/create
**** Edit: /admin/buffet-dinners/edit/:id
*** Buffet Bookings: /admin/buffet-bookings
*** Membership Tiers
**** List: /admin/membership-tiers
**** Create: /admin/membership-tiers/create
**** Edit: /admin/membership-tiers/edit/:id
*** Reviews: /admin/reviews
@endwbs
